	"@You're on your way to Giant Step, aren't you?" next
	"@Just be careful, the police are pretty touchy about people," next
	"@not to mention kids, going up there..."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70688:
	"@The police were here looking for you.  Did you do something illegal?" next
	"@Head south on the street in front of my shop.  You'll find the Onett Police Station." next
	"@I think it's best if you turn yourself in... no matter what you may have done."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70711:
	"@Have you heard of a girl named {name(2)}?" next
	"@She lives in Twoson, the town next to Onett..." next
	"@They say she has some pretty spectacular supernatural powers." next
	"@You can get to Twoson by heading south."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70789:
	"@Have you been to Apple Kid and Orange Kid's houses?" next
	"@Their places are south of the Polestar Preschool." next
	"@They are great inventors ...to be." next
	"@They need some financial help." next
	"@If you help them ...later," next
	"@for sure," next
	"@without fail," next
	"@certainly," next
	"@something wonderful will happen." next
	"@Believe me, this hint is worth a lot more than you paid."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70868:
	"@If you go east from the bus stop," next
	"@you will enter the Grateful Dead Valley." next
	"@If you keep going east, you will come to Happy Happy Village." next
	"@You should maybe go there, unless you have something better to do?"
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc708dd:
	"@You got a call from Apple Kid on your Receiver phone?" next
	"@What are you doing here, so far away from his home?" next
	"@I can't give you any hints, but I'll keep your ${number(0)}."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70943:
	"@Have you spoken to Everdred in Burglin Park?" linebreak
	two_choice_menu("Yes", l_0xc709ac, "No", l_0xc70974)

l_0xc70974:
	"@Well, well, well...  That's not good." next
	"@You really should take the time out to meet Everdred."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc709ac:
	"@What?  You DID talk to him?  So, why are you here?" next
	"@Go back to the Grateful Dead Valley."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc709e8:
	"@Have you been to the Happy Happyism headquarters" next
	"@at the center of Happy Happy Village?" next
	"@Do you want to go there?" next
	"@Or not?" next
	"@What?" next
	"@Why can't you make up your mind!"
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70a4c:
	"@Do you remember seeing a litte mountain cabin on the way" next
	"@through the Grateful Dead Valley?" next
	"@There must be a cave in the Happy Happy Village that leads to that cabin."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70ab5:
	"@This is my business, so I'm happy to have customers." next
	"@But, don't you know this is a crisis?" pause(20)
	"  You shouldn't be wasting time here." next
	"@Anyway, I'll keep your ${number(0)}."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70b17:
	"@You know that {name(2)} is in the mountain cabin, right?" next
	"@By rescuing her, you actually rescue yourself."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70b59:
	"@{name(2)}'s father at the Polestar Preschool must be really worried." next
	"@You should be considerate of a father's feelings toward his daughter." next
	"@He's only human, y'know!"
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70bc4:
	"@Go and see Everdred, the boss of Burglin Park." next
	"@Just trust me... you go see him."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70bff:
	"@The Runaway Brothers, the band at the Chaos theater, is up to their eyes in debt." next
	"@Could anyone pay off their debt for them?"
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70c4d:
	"@I don't think there is anything else you need to do in this town." next
	"@It's okay if you stay, but it's really okay if you leave..."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70c8d:
	"@There's a tunnel northwest of this town." next
	"@There are two guard zombies that hang out at the entrance." next
	"@They are actually pretty nice guys..." next
	"@It might be a good idea to meet those guys..." next
	"@But it's quite all right if you don't..." next
	"@Though I think that you really ought to go there."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70d2f:
	"@So, how are you doin', kid?" next
	"@If you're tired, you should go to the hotel and rest."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70d5f:
	"@Do you know about that mysterious tent that appeared" next
	"@at the south end of town?" next
	"@I don't know, but..." linebreak
	"  it looks kinda..." linebreak
	"  strange..."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70db0:
	call(data_29.l_0xc72620)
	eob

l_0xc70db6:
	"@<Zombie Paper only works well in a tent.>" next
	"@<After you set the paper in a tent, go to the hotel and put your dogs up.>" next
	"@What, didn't you read the Zombie paper instructions?"
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70e26:
	"@There's an underground path northwest of this town." next
	"@Those guard zombies should be gone now."
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70e61:
	"@|Saturn Valley is very nice!" linebreak
	"  You should go" linebreak
	"  at least once or twice|"
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70e95:
	"@It seems like you don't know what to do in Saturn Valley." next
	"@The Mr. Saturn on the second floor of the cave should be able to tell you" next
	"@a password to get you into the secret base." next
	"@Now that sounds like some handy info!"
	call(data_29.l_0xc726cb)
	eob

l_0xc70f16:
	"@Mr. Saturn must have told you to wait for three minutes in front of the waterfall." next
	"@What?  You don't know where the waterfall is?" next
	"@The waterfall is actually named Grapefruit Falls." next
	"@After you exit the tunnel that begins in the Threek graveyard," next
	"@go to the north." next
	"@You certainly know about the cave to Saturn Valley that is then on your right." next
	"@But..." linebreak
	"  You should not go in that cave." next
	"@Keep going straight north." next
	"@You'll eventually come to the Grapefruit Falls." next
	"@Then, wait patiently for three minutes."
